data.description: Welcome to 24884 Cold Canyon Trail located in the beautiful Audie Murphy Ranch community! This amazing turn key home offers 2624 SQFT of living space with 4 bedrooms, 3 a half bathrooms and a large loft upstairs. The Master bedroom as well as two bedrooms are located downstairs. A large bedroom & full bath along with a large sized loft are located upstairs. With top of the line upgrades with laminate flooring downstairs and beautiful tile work in the bathrooms as well as the backsplash in the kitchen, which is also equipped with all stainless steel appliances that look amazing combined with the quartz countertops. The kitchen also offers a large quartz countertop island equipped with a sink. This home comes with a whole house fan great for the hot summer days, a great backyard for bbq's and to spend time with family & friends and your own putting green. Located very close to one of the HOA pools, The Plunge, a block from the sports park and access to all amenities such as pools, spas, sports courts, skate park, hiking/biking trails, the club house, and the award winning Taawila ES, new Kathryn Newport MS and between the 15 and 215 fwys. This is a must-see property!
